<collectingCountry id="F31E7642FFCDFFCCF690FDE1EFA7FD96" box="[2395,2458,598,623]" name="Laos" pageId="8" pageNumber="415">Laos</collectingCountry>
and Vietnam but may be extinct there now.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BB636D2FFCDFFCCF82DFD2BEEDCFD1C" blockId="8.[2021,2607,279,701]" lastBlockId="8.[1405,2609,716,2236]" pageId="8" pageNumber="415">
Tt was introduced some centuries ago in 
